      0.24553571407647,
      0.4887218005225646,
      0.27480158746227146
    ],
    "page": "exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2009_Solutions_2009s_page_002",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "docling_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_2009_Solutions_2009s_page_002_5",
    "text": "For any nonnegative integer m, the elements of G of order at most 2\" form a subgroup isomorphic to",
